{{version029}}
{{flavour|Binds the caster to nearby allies, redirecting half of any damage they suffer to the caster.}}

'''Injury Bond''' is a monster-only spell that protects nearby allies, causing half of any damage dealt to an ally to instead affect the caster. This redirected damage can eventually kill the caster, ending the effect immediately.

{{monsters with spell}}

Players can protect their allies by [[Summon Guardian Golem|summoning]] a [[guardian golem]].

==History==
*Injury Bond was added in [[0.12]].

[[Category:Monster spells]]
